            <title><![CDATA[News Wrap: Judge orders Kennedy Center to remove Trump's name from building]]></title>
            <link>https://www.pbs.org/newshour/show/news-wrap-judge-orders-kennedy-center-to-remove-trumps-name-from-building</link>
            <description><![CDATA[In our news wrap Friday, a federal judge ordered the Kennedy Center to remove Donald Trump's name from the building, the U.S. and Iran appear to still be far apart on a potential deal to end the conflict and Romania says that a Russian drone crashed into an apartment building near its border with Ukraine, the first known time that's happened on NATO soil since Russia invaded Ukraine.]]></description>
